Frances Nash, Individually and as Executrix of Edward M. Nash, Deceased, Respondent, v. Max Frank, Individually and as Executor of Louis B. Frank, Deceased, et al., Appellants, et al., Defendant.

Judgment and orders so far as appealed from unanimously affirmed, with costs to the respondent. No opinion. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Rabin, Frank and Stevens, JJ.
